<div class="postcell post-layout--right">
    <div class="post-text" itemprop="text">

<p>When I copy code from another file, the formatting is messed up, like this:</p>

<pre><code>fun()
{
for(...)
{
for(...)
{
if(...)
{
}
}
}
}
</code></pre>

<p>How can I autoformat this code in vim?</p>
