            </div>
            


<div class="answercell post-layout--right">
    <div class="post-text" itemprop="text">
<p>I find that <code>clang-format</code> works well.</p>

<p>There are some example keybindings in the <a href="http://clang.llvm.org/docs/ClangFormat.html" rel="noreferrer">clang documentation</a></p>

<p>I prefer to use the <code>equalprg</code> binding in vim. This allows you to invoke <code>clang-format</code> with <code>G=gg</code> or other <code>=</code> indent options.</p>

<p>Just put the following in your .vimrc file:</p>

<pre><code>autocmd FileType c,cpp setlocal equalprg=clang-format
</code></pre>
    </div>
